<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span>فِي الرَّد بِهِ<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>إِلَّا أَن يسْتَند إِلَى سَبَب مُتَقَدم<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>يجهله المُشْتَرِي<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
